						<p><font size="3"><b>In 1935, Saint-Beno&icirc;t-du-Lac became an autonomous house. In 1938, the monks decided to build a monastery and Dom Paul Bellot, renowned architect, was asked to draw the plans. The new buildings were blessed on July 11th 1941.</b></font></td>
					<td width="2" height="145"></td>
